So, no more hacks and workarounds, the `JsonType` will work no matter what DB you are using.

If you want to see it in action, check out [this test folder on GitHub](https://github.com/vladmihalcea/hypersistence-utils/tree/master/hypersistence-utils-hibernate-55/src/test/java/io/hypersistence/utils/hibernate/type/json/generic).

